<h4 id="goal-setting">Goal Setting:</h4>

<p>In my last post I talked about going towards your fears.  For me, that is roofs on gear since I took a huge, life threatening, whipper almost 
one year ago.  In one of the recent <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Board Meetings</code> on the <a href="http://www.powercompanyclimbing.com/podcast/">Power Company Climbing podcast</a> I heard Kris Hampton talk about treating trad redpoints link sport climbs.  Interestingly enough, I had gifted the Anderson brothersâ€™ <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Rock-Climbers-Training-Manual/dp/0989515613">Rock Climberâ€™s Training 
